                <p><strong>Why "$5K-worth"?</strong> Agency discovery phases (industry analysis + business audit + strategic recommendations) typically cost $2,000-$5,000 for comparable scope. By collapsing the drafting phase, I produced equivalent deliverables in one afternoon.</p>
                <p>The leverage isn't "AI does my thinking." It's <strong>"AI does my drafting, so I can focus on thinking and verification."</strong></p>

